The '''Embassy of the State of Palestine''' in the [[North Korea| Democratic People's Republic of Korea]] ({{lang-ar|سفارة دولة فلسطين لدى كوريا الشمالية}}) is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[State of Palestine|Palestine]] in North Korea. It is located in [[Munsudong]], [[Taedonggang District]], [[Pyongyang]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mofa.pna.ps/ar/archives/3257|title=Embassy of the State of Palestine in |publisher=Ministry of foreign affairs of State of Palestine|accessdate=23 March 2017}}</ref>

